<i>noun</i>: 곤두박질 [곤두박찔] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>곤두박질 [곤두박찔]</dt><br>
<dd>1. falling headlong; falling head-first</dd><br>
<dd>갑자기 거꾸로 떨어지거나 아래로 내리박힘.</dd><br>
<dd>Taking a sudden fall or falling head-first to the ground.</dd><br>
<dd>2. plummeting</dd><br>
<dd>좋지 않은 상태로 급격히 떨어짐.</dd><br>
<dd>Suddenly falling into a bad situation.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>